abstract:
  The B\"acklund transformation and its nonlinear superposition principle are
presented for the Krichever-Novikov equation $u_t= u_{xxx} - {3/(2u_x)}
(u^2_{xx} - r(u)) + cu_x, r^{(5)}=0$.

authors:
R. Prozorov, A. Poddar, E. Sheriff, A. Shaulov, Y. Yeshurun (Institute
  for Superconductivity, Physics Department, Bar-Ilan University, Ramat-Gan,
  Israel)

